Hello all, this is the first entry of the one and only wonderful Toe Jelly This entire blog is dedicated to my obsession with shoes and micelanious pictures of feet... All taken by ME! Huzzah! [I would like to add that I do not have a foot fetish, or any abnormal fettish for that matter, shoes are just cool] so... ENJOY! ...

What better way to start this blog than pics of my own feet?!

♥Toe Jelly

[sorry I didn't get this one up til so late, I was selling artwork all day at a fair and I'm exausted] I absolutely love this pic! I took this at a gig I played a few months back with Alien Lunchbox [who rock and yew should look up on myspace] There's just something that humors me about a 200+ pound bald [yet hary legged] bass player wearing bright pink converse ♥ -Toe Jelly
